import Link from 'next/link'

import {
  Nav,
  NavContainer,
  NavRow,
  LinkStyled,
  NavList,
  NavListItem,
  NavItemLink,
  NavItemText,
} from './header.styles'

export const Header = () => {
  return (
    <Nav>
      <NavContainer>
        <NavRow>
          <LinkStyled href="/">
            Logo
          </LinkStyled>
          <NavList>
            <NavListItem>
              <Link href="/projects">
                <NavItemLink>
                  <NavItemText data-hover="Projects">
                    Projects
                  </NavItemText>
                </NavItemLink>
              </Link>
              <Link href="/contact">
                <NavItemLink>
                  <NavItemText data-hover="Contact">
                    Contact
                  </NavItemText>
                </NavItemLink>
              </Link>
            </NavListItem>
          </NavList>
        </NavRow>
      </NavContainer>
    </Nav>
  )
}
